 <a name="71106-0001.htm_para12"></a>
-<p><a name="stpa_12"></a><a name="0711069000023"></a>&#147;There will be a Bill to improve services for vulnerable children and young people, including those in care.</p>
+<p><a name="stpa_12"></a><a name="0711069000023"></a>There will be a Bill to improve services for vulnerable children and young people, including those in care.</p>
 
 <a name="71106-0001.htm_para13"></a>
-<p><a name="stpa_13"></a><a name="0711069000024"></a>&#147;My Government will bring forward proposals to help people achieve a better balance between work and family life.</p>
