 <a name="71106-0001.htm_para22"></a>
-<p><a name="stpa_22"></a><a name="0711069000033"></a>&#147;My Government will publish a draft Bill on citizenship.</p>
+<p><a name="stpa_22"></a><a name="0711069000033"></a>My Government will publish a draft Bill on citizenship.</p>
 
 
 
 
